text: The Swedish Shooting Sport Federation (, SvSF) is a Swedish sport shooting association founded in 2009 by merging the three former organisations Swedish Sport Shooting Association (Svenska Sportskytteförbundet, SSF), Frivilliga Skytterörelsen (FSR) and Skytterörelsens Ungdomsorganisation (Skytte UO).FSR is now discontinued - the Swedish Shooting Association (FSR är nu avvecklat - Svenska Skyttesportförbundet) == See also == * Swedish Dynamic Sports Shooting Association * Norwegian Shooting Association * Det frivillige Skyttervesen * Danish Gymnastics and Sports Associations == References == == External links == * Official website of the Swedish Shooting Sport Federation Category:2009 establishments Category:Shooting sports organizations Shooting
title: Swedish Shooting Sport Federation
